There was apprehension in the early hours of Tuesday when Sunday Igboho’s house in Ibadan was gutted by fire. The true cause of the fire is yet to be ascertained. However, according to the information gathered when Tribune Online visited the scene, the incident was the work of arsonists. A source said the hoodlums shot around the area, a situation which lasted for about an hour. According to him, the hoodlums came around 2a.m and left around past 3 am. He said, thankfully, no life was lost.  More details to come… WATCH THE VIDEO:    SEE THE PHOTOS HERE  SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE TO GET IT!!!